data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Step inside to discover open concept living room area for relaxation or gatherings. The eat in kitchen is equipped with stainless steal appliances. Enjoy the convenience of a new tankless water heater installed in 2022 and comes with a 10 year transferrable warranty. Outside, the expansive yard beckons for outdoor activities and entertaining. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to make this your dream home.
